Nutrient data for: CADBURY HIGHLIGHTS CHOCOLATE DRINK CHOCOLATE 220 GR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622300751395

Ingredients: Fat-reduced cocoa powder (26%), whey powder (from MILK), skimmed MILK powder, inulin, milk chocolate (6%) [MILK, sugar, cocoa mass, cocoa butter, vegetable oils (palm and shea in various proportions), emulsifiers (E442, sunflower lecithin), flavourings], glucose syrup, palm oil, thickener (E407), flavouring, salt, MILK proteins, anti-caking agent (E551), sweetener (aspartame, acesulfame K), emulsifier (E471).Cocoa, Sugar: traded in compliance with Fairtrade Standards.
